Glitch effect with OpenGL/C++

----------------------------------CREDITS--------------------------------------
Billy the Puppet 3d model by paulyanez
https://sketchfab.com/paulyanez

------------------------------------USAGE--------------------------------------

To compile:
	$ make

To load scene:
	$ ./glitch [path]

Examples:
	$ ./glitch resources/img.jpg
	$ ./glitch resources/jigsaw/source/jigsaw.obj

ONLY jpg and obj files are accepted!
